<h2 id="About_Solr">  About Solr </h2>
Solr is an open source enterprise search server based on the <span class='externalLink'><a href="http://lucene.apache.org">Lucene</a></span> Java search
library, with XML/HTTP and JSON APIs, hit highlighting, faceted search,
caching, replication, and a web administration interface. 
<p></p>

