<h4 id="SOLRFORMAT">  SOLRFORMAT </h4>
<p></p>

When a solr response has been cached using the <code>id</code> parameter to <a class="foswikiCurrentTopicLink" href="#SOLRSEARCH">SOLRSEARCH</a>, it can be reused by subsequent calls to %SOLRFORMAT.
<p></p>

<pre class="tml">
&#37;SOLRSEARCH{&#34;test&#34; 
  id&#61;&#34;solr1&#34;
  facets&#61;&#34;web,contributor&#34;
  facetlimit&#61;&#34;web&#61;10, contributor&#61;10&#34;
}&#37;

&#60;noautolink&#62;
&#42;Results:&#42;
&#37;SOLRFORMAT{&#34;solr1&#34;
  format&#61;&#34;   1 &#91;&#91;&#36;web.&#36;topic&#93;&#91;&#36;topic&#93;&#93;&#36;n&#34;
}&#37;

&#42;Webs:&#42;
&#37;SOLRFORMAT{&#34;solr1&#34;
  format&#95;web&#61;&#34;   &#42; &#36;key (&#36;count)&#36;n&#34;
}&#37;

&#42;Contributors:&#42;
&#37;SOLRFORMAT{&#34;solr1&#34;
  format&#95;contributor&#61;&#34;   &#42; &#36;key (&#36;count)&#36;n&#34;
  exclude&#95;contributor&#61;&#34;UnknownUser&#124;AdminGroup&#124;AdminUser&#124;RegistrationAgent&#124;TestUser&#34;
}&#37;
&#60;/noautolink&#62;
</pre>
<p></p>

