		</tr>
		<tr class="foswikiTableOdd foswikiTableRowdataBgSorted0 foswikiTableRowdataBg0">
			<td class="foswikiTableCol0 foswikiFirstCol" style="text-align:right"> 17 Jul 2015: </td>
			<td class="foswikiTableCol1 foswikiLastCol"> added support for Foswiki-2.0 ;                  indexing workflow and state facets supporting <a class="interwikiLink" href="https://foswiki.org/Extensions/WorkflowPlugin" title="'Extensions/WorkflowPlugin' on foswiki.org">Foswiki:Extensions/WorkflowPlugin</a>;                   added <code>author_url</code> to solr schema;                   added google image and video mime types mapping them to "image" while indexing </td>
		</tr>
		<tr class="foswikiTableEven foswikiTableRowdataBgSorted1 foswikiTableRowdataBg1">
